harfbuzz
------------------------------------------
HarfBuzz is an OpenType text shaping engine.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.7-1
  libfreetype6-2.3.12-1
  libgcc1-4.3.4-3
  libglib2.0_0-2.24.1-1
  libicu45-4.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-9-1
  automake-4-10
  binutils-2.20.51-2
  cygport-0.10.2-1
  gawk-3.1.8-1
  gcc4-core-4.3.4-3
  libtool-2.4-1
  make-3.81-2

Canonical website:
  http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/HarfBuzz

Canonical download:
  harfbuzz-0.3.20101222git.tar.bz2 

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack harfbuzz-0.3.20101222git-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./harfbuzz-0.3.20101222git-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/harfbuzz-0.3.20101222git-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/harfbuzz-0.3.20101222git-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libharfbuzz0-0.3.20101222git-X.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/libharfbuzz-devel-0.3.20101222git-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

